name: .BSXC File Extension
summary: Learn about .BSXC files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can import a BSXC file into BimSens (Windows). To do so, create or select a relevant project component (e.g. a data source component if your BSXC file was created from a data source) and then select Import from the component's configuration dialogue.
